&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://blog.reincarnatey.net/2023/build-hugo-blog-with-stack-mod/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>建站技术 | 使用 Hugo + Stack 简单搭建一个博客&lt;/a>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Tools Trick</title><link>https://sleepman9.github.io/p/tools-trick/</link><pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://sleepman9.github.io/p/tools-trick/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://sleepman9.github.io/p/tools-trick/cover.jpg" alt="Featured image of post Tools Trick" />&lt;h2 id="1-vscode中github-copilot在ssh远程环境中无法登录问题">1. VSCode中Github Copilot在SSH远程环境中无法登录问题
